<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>C++ on Hello World 大冒險</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/tags/c++/</link><description>Recent content in C++ on Hello World 大冒險</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-tw</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 03 Jun 2023 03:02:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/tags/c++/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>SDL2 環境配置</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/06/03/sdl2-%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</link><pubDate>Sat, 03 Jun 2023 03:02:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/06/03/sdl2-%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/index.png" alt="Featured image of post SDL2 環境配置" />&lt;h1 id="下載-sdl2">下載 SDL2&lt;/h1>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>pacman -S mingw-w64-x86_64-SDL2
mingw-w64-x86_64-SDL2_gfx
mingw-w64-x86_64-SDL2_image
mingw-w64-x86_64-SDL2_mixer
mingw-w64-x86_64-SDL2_net
mingw-w64-x86_64-SDL2_ttf
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h1 id="編譯參數">編譯參數&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>在 &lt;code>.vscode\tasks.json&lt;/code> 中，照順序添加四個參數&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>&amp;quot;args&amp;quot;: [
&amp;quot;-fdiagnostics-color=always&amp;quot;,
&amp;quot;-g&amp;quot;,
&amp;quot;${file}&amp;quot;,
&amp;quot;-lmingw32&amp;quot;, //參數1
&amp;quot;-mwindows&amp;quot;, //參數2
&amp;quot;-lSDL2main&amp;quot;, //參數3
&amp;quot;-lSDL2&amp;quot;, //參數4
&amp;quot;-o&amp;quot;,
&amp;quot;${fileDirname}\\${fileBasenameNoExtension}.exe&amp;quot;
],&lt;/code>&lt;/pre></description></item><item><title>C++ 環境配置</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/31/c-%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 May 2023 01:53:02 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/31/c-%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/31/c-%E7%92%B0%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/index.png" alt="Featured image of post C++ 環境配置" />&lt;h1 id="安裝-msys2">安裝 MSYS2&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://www.msys2.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>下載連結&lt;/a>&lt;br>
如果沒有要更改安裝位置的話，持續點擊下一步就好&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="更新">更新&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>打開 MSYS2&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>pacman -Syu
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h1 id="下載-mingw-w64">下載 mingw-w64&lt;/h1>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>pacman -S mingw-w64-ucrt-x86_64-gcc
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h1 id="下載--mingw-w64-工具組">下載 mingw-w64 工具組&lt;/h1>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>pacman -S --needed base-devel mingw-w64-x86_64-toolchain
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;h1 id="新增環境變數">新增環境變數&lt;/h1>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>複製 &lt;code>mingw-w64&lt;/code> 中 &lt;code>bin&lt;/code> 的路徑 ( 預設安裝路徑 : &lt;code>C:\msys64\mingw64\bin&lt;/code> )&lt;/li>
&lt;li>設定 &amp;gt; 系統 &amp;gt; 系統資訊 &amp;gt; 進階系統設定 &amp;gt; 進階 &amp;gt; 環境變數 &amp;gt; Path&lt;/li>
&lt;li>將 &lt;code>C:\msys64\mingw64\bin&lt;/code> 新增至 &lt;code>Path&lt;/code> 中&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h1 id="檢查">檢查&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>如果沒有出現奇怪的東西，就表示成功了&lt;/p>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>gcc --version
g++ --version
gdb --version
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre></description></item><item><title>C++ 俄羅斯方塊(TCP連線對戰)</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/24/c-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%A1%8Atcp%E9%80%A3%E7%B7%9A%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%B0/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 May 2023 04:03:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/24/c-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%A1%8Atcp%E9%80%A3%E7%B7%9A%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%B0/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/24/c-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E6%96%B9%E5%A1%8Atcp%E9%80%A3%E7%B7%9A%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%B0/index.png" alt="Featured image of post C++ 俄羅斯方塊(TCP連線對戰)" /></description></item><item><title>C++ 跳動的愛心</title><link>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/24/c-%E8%B7%B3%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 May 2023 04:02:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/24/c-%E8%B7%B3%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://huihsiang9292.github.io/2023/05/24/c-%E8%B7%B3%E5%8B%95%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83/index.png" alt="Featured image of post C++ 跳動的愛心" /></description></item></channel></rss>